	(235,1,'2015-08-26 02:22:25','2015-08-26 02:22:25','<!--:en--><div id=\"area-article-first-block\" class=\"area\">\r\n<div id=\"mod-a-body-first-para\" class=\"mod-economictimesarticletext mod-articletext\">\r\n\r\nASUS has officially unveiled a new 256GB model of the ZenFone 2 Deluxe at a dedicated launch event in Sao Paulo, Brazil. This version packs the same hardware as the initially unveiled model and the internal storage is the only differentiating factor here.\r\n\r\nThis takes smartphone storage to a whole new level and ensures that users don\'t have to be looking for a microSD card to get more storage on their handset. It is not known as to when the smartphone will be unveiled in the Indian markets, but we\'re guessing that will happen very soon knowing that the ZenFone 2 was one of the first markets where the ZenFone 2 Deluxe was announced and released.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--:-->','<!--:en-->ASUS Releases a 256GB Storage<!--:-->','','publish','open','open','','asus-releases-a-256gb-storage-variant-of-the-zenfone-2-deluxe','','','2015-09-01 02:24:23','2015-09-01 02:24:23','',0,'http://asus-zenpad.stagingapps.net/?p=235',0,'post','',0),
