iled audio, whether you\'re listening through the tablet\'s speakers or your headphones. This crystal-clear, expansive audio experience was tuned by sound experts in the Asus Golden Ear team.\r\n\r\nFeel the need to turn up the volume and spruce up the sound effects at a house party? Cord-cutters will appreciate the Asus Audio Cover, the world\'s first 5.1-channel surround sound accessory that packs four satellite speakers, one center-channel speaker and a subwoofer! This takes cord-cutting to the next level, delivering a truly mobile movie experience on your own terms.\r\n\r\nIt\'s common for cord-cutters to fret over running out of juice while watching movies on a tablet. With up to six hours of battery life on a single charge, the ZenPad lets you watch two to three movies, or about half the season of House of Cards at one go - if you\'re into binge-watching.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_image=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"\" alignment=\"\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" css_animation=\"\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"\"]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"\" alignment=\"\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" css_animation=\"\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"\"]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing